<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Mercy College will award a maximum of nine credit hours through AP provided that the student achieves a rating of at least 3 (equivalent to a grade of &quot;C &quot;) on each test for which credit is desired.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.mchs.edu/pdf/2011-12Catalog_Final.pdf" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
